ìíŸ@42d52a66ed1ee113a57da715be68d11ab94b2f4be15497de0813143a28745e5a⁄}Title: This week in Nushell #178
Path: Nushell
Content:
WindSoilder 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/7675] made 
``save``
 stream on list stream data
webbedspace 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/7798] updated 
``help <cmd>``
 to not list deprecated subcommands
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/7752] ``str length``
, 
``str substring``
, 
``str index-of``
, 
``split words``
 and 
``split chars``
 now use graphemes instead of UTF-8 bytes
merelymyself created 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/7789] let 
``find``
 take linebreaks into account in 
``Value::String``
fdncred 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/7802] fixed signature display in help commands
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/7772] update sqlparser dependency
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/7771] update semver dep
zschaffer 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/7785] added magenta to ansi command as synonym for purple
1Kinoti 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/7784] added dedicated 
``const in pipeline``
, 
``const builtin var``
 errors
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/7759] Allow underscores in integers and floats
Xoffio 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/7779] fixed Issue 7648 which crashes nushell and happens when an alias name is shorter than the alias command and the alias command is an external command.
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/7756] Add test for fix of issue #7754
DaRacci updated 
``cd``
 to 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/7775] check all user groups
hustcer 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/7773] fixed some typos
afetisov 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/7755] fixed typos and used more idiomatic assertions
NotLebedev created a new 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/7751] ansi link
 command
VincenzoCarlino 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/7702] renamed the 
``to url``
 command to 
``url build-query``
rgwood created 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/7619] LazyRecord
 to speed up startup
